POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (33): PAKISTAN (KHYBER PAKHTUNKHWA TRIBAL DISTRICTS, SINDH) NEW CASE, FOLLOW-UP ON PREVIOUSLY CONFIRMED CASE, REQUEST FOR INFORMATION
**********************************************************************************************************************************************************
